			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="The player has been spotted by one of the statues that control the traps at the Shar Temple's main junction. The player is trapped in a room and has an item taken from them as 'punishment'. Note that this trap is more of a training challenge for Shar recruits than it is a security system." />
